channel.title: Revenge of the Iron-Blooded Sword Hound
channel.description: [By the studio that brought you , , and many more!] He was the hound of the Baskerville family: Vikir.Yet his loyalty was rewarded by the blade of a guillotine dirtied by slander."I will never live the life of a hound slaughtered after the rabbit is caught."In place of death, an unexpected opportunity awaits him.Vikir's eyes glowed red as he sharpened his canines in the dark."Just you wait, Hugo. I will rip out your throat this time."It's time for the hound to exact bloody revenge on his owner.
